rAge 2018, which takes place from 5-7 October 2018, has official ticket pricing. The event will be hosted at the Ticketpro Dome in Johannesburg and will feature a variety of gaming and geek-related activities. Tickets for the expo will be available from Computicket from 1 May 2018 and will be priced as follows: Tickets to the NAG BYOC LAN will go on sale from 28 July 2018, and prices have not yet been confirmed. rAge 2018 is the largest event in the country focused on PC and console gaming, esports, cosplay, and multiple facets of geek culture.